"""
AWS Lambda function that scrapes the GMU School of Computing catalog
and writes structured .txt files to S3 for use as an LLM knowledge base.

Features:
- Scrapes school overview, department overviews, faculty, courses, and program pages
- Expands manual program coverage
- Auto-discovers additional program links from department pages
- Uses retries + session headers
- Writes clean text files to S3
"""

